comment.body:
Find that the bitmessage address looks quite ugly. You can add this block of code to `/path/to/yourblog/css/all.css` to solve it ;)
```
.left p {
word-break: break-all;
}
```
Also here is [my tech blog](/1EiMAqhd6sMjPG2tznkkGXxhdwFBDdeqT9/), have been blogging on ZeroNet for more than half a year, feel free to take a visit 

Edit:
`break-all` breaks normal word as long as it reaches the right border. Better solution:
```
.left p code {
max-width: 100%;
word-wrap: break-word;
padding: 2px 2px;
}
```
